          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">M</hi>Y neighbour <hi rend="italics">Hunks</hi>'s house and mine</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-2" n="2">Are built so near, they almost join;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-3" n="3">The windows too project so much,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-4" n="4">That thro' the casements we may touch:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-5" n="5">Nay, I'm so happy, most men think,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-6" n="6">To live so near a man of chink,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-7" n="7">That they are apt to envy me,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-8" n="8">For keeping such good company.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-9" n="9">But he's as far from me, I vow,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-10" n="10">As <hi rend="italics">London</hi> is from good lord <hi rend="italics">Howe</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-11" n="11">Who sooths the poor <hi rend="italics">Barbadoes</hi> folks,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-12" n="12">All gall'd and raw with <hi rend="italics">L────r</hi>'s yokes.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-13" n="13">For when old <hi rend="italics">Hunks</hi> I chance to meet,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-14" n="14"><hi rend="italics">Or</hi> one or both must quit the street.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-15" n="15">Thus, he who would not see old <hi rend="italics">Roger</hi>,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y54D37L1-line-16" n="16">Must be his neighbour, or his lodger.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
